remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-103">此類型已被取代，並將.NET Framework 的未來版本中移除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-103">This type is deprecated and will be removed in a future version of the .NET Framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-104">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 < [Oracle 和 ADO.NET](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/oracle-and-adonet.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-104">For more information, see [Oracle and ADO.NET](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/oracle-and-adonet.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-105"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>做為橋樑**資料集**和用來擷取並儲存資料的資料庫。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-105">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> serves as a bridge between a **DataSet** and database for retrieving and saving data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-106"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>藉由使用提供此橋接器<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A>將資料從資料庫載入<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，並使用<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>傳送中所做的變更<xref:System.Data.DataSet>回資料來源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-106">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> provides this bridge by using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> to load data from the database into the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, and using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A> to send changes made in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> back to the data source.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-107">當<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>填滿<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，它會建立必要的資料表和資料行傳回的資料如果它們尚不存在。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-107">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> fills a <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, it creates the necessary tables and columns for the returned data if they do not already exist.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-108">不過，主索引鍵資訊不會納入以隱含方式建立的結構描述除非<xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A>屬性設定為<xref:System.Data.MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-108">However, primary key information is not included in the implicitly created schema unless the <xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Data.MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-109">您也可以<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>建立的結構描述<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，包括主索引鍵資訊的詳細資訊，再填入資料使用<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-109">You may also have the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> create the schema of the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, including primary key information, before filling it with data using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-110">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> [ 將現有條件約束加入至資料集](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/adding-existing-constraints-to-a-dataset.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-110">For more information, see [Adding Existing Constraints to a DataSet](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/adding-existing-constraints-to-a-dataset.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="30aea-111">根據預設，數值欄位，匯入至<xref:System.Data.DataTable>具有<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A>對應至<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-111">By default, numeric fields imported to a <xref:System.Data.DataTable> with <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> are mapped to <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-112">就能夠溢位<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>，並藉由匯入非整數數字的值太大或太高精確度的擲回 Oracle 例外狀況，<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>的有效位數的限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-112">It is possible to overflow the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>, and throw an Oracle exception, by importing a non-integral numeric value that is either too large or too high precision for the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>'s precision limitations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-113">描述，請參閱<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>如需詳細資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-113">Refer to the description of <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber> for more information.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-114"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>也包含<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>， <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>， <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>， <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>，和`TableMappings`屬性，以加速載入和更新的資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-114">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> also includes the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>, and `TableMappings` properties to facilitate loading and updating of data.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-115">.NET Framework Data Provider for Oracle 不支援批次的 SQL 陳述式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-115">The .NET Framework Data Provider for Oracle does not support batched SQL statements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-116">不過，它允許您使用多個`REF CURSOR`輸出參數來填滿**資料集**，在它自己的每個<xref:System.Data.DataTable>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-116">However, it does allow you to use multiple `REF CURSOR` output parameters to fill a **DataSet**, each in its own <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-117">您必須定義參數、 將它們標示為輸出參數，並指出它們屬於`REF CURSOR`資料型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-117">You must define the parameters, mark them as output parameters, and indicate that they are `REF CURSOR` data types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-118">請注意，您無法使用<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>方法時<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>填滿使用`REF CURSOR`傳回預存程序中，因為 Oracle 不提供必要資訊，以判斷哪些資料表名稱和資料行名稱的參數執行 SQL 陳述式時。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-118">Note that you cannot use the <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A> method when the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> is filled using `REF CURSOR` parameters returned by a stored procedure, because Oracle does not provide the information necessary to determine what the table name and column names are when the SQL statement is executed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-119">下列 C# 範例會假設您已建立此預存程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-119">The following C# example assumes that you have created this stored procedure.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-120">在 Oracle 伺服器上建立下列 Oracle 封裝。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-120">Create the following Oracle package on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
```  
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE CURSPKG AS   
   TYPE T_CURSOR IS REF CURSOR;   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
      IO_CURSOR OUT T_CURSOR);   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
      DEPTCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR);  
END CURSPKG;  
/  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-121">在 Oracle 伺服器上建立下列 Oracle Package 內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-121">Create the following Oracle package body on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
```  
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CURSPKG AS   
    PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
                               IO_CURSOR OUT T_CURSOR)   
    IS   
        V_CURSOR T_CURSOR;   
    BEGIN   
        IF N_EMPNO <> 0 THEN   
             OPEN V_CURSOR FOR   
             SELECT EMP.EMPNO, EMP.ENAME, DEPT.DEPTNO, DEPT.DNAME   
                  FROM EMP, DEPT   
                  WHERE EMP.DEPTNO = DEPT.DEPTNO   
                        AND EMP.EMPNO = N_EMPNO;   
        ELSE   
             OPEN V_CURSOR FOR   
             SELECT EMP.EMPNO, EMP.ENAME, DEPT.DEPTNO, DEPT.DNAME   
                  FROM EMP, DEPT   
                  WHERE EMP.DEPTNO = DEPT.DEPTNO;   
        END IF;   
        IO_CURSOR := V_CURSOR;   
    END OPEN_ONE_CURSOR;   
    PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
                                DEPTCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR)   
    IS   
        V_CURSOR1 T_CURSOR;   
        V_CURSOR2 T_CURSOR;   
    BEGIN   
        OPEN V_CURSOR1 FOR SELECT * FROM EMP;   
        OPEN V_CURSOR2 FOR SELECT * FROM DEPT;   
        EMPCURSOR  := V_CURSOR1;   
        DEPTCURSOR := V_CURSOR2;   
    END OPEN_TWO_CURSORS;   
END CURSPKG;  
 /  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-122">下列 C# 範例示範如何取得使用預存程序的資料表和資料行資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-122">The following C# example demonstrates how you might obtain table and column information using the stored procedure.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// GetConnectionString() returns a connection string for  
// the data source.  
  
string connString = GetConnectionString();  
DataSet ds = new DataSet();  
OracleConnection conn = new OracleConnection(connString);  
OracleCommand cmd = conn.CreateCommand();  
  
cmd.CommandText = "CURSPKG.OPEN_TWO_CURSORS";  
cmd.CommandType = CommandType.StoredProcedure;  
cmd.Parameters.Add("EMPCURSOR", OracleType.Cursor).Direction =   
       ParameterDirection.Output;  
cmd.Parameters.Add("DEPTCURSOR", OracleType.Cursor).Direction =   
       ParameterDirection.Output;  
  
OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter(cmd);  
da.TableMappings.Add("Table", "Emp");  
da.TableMappings.Add("Table1", "Dept");  
da.Fill(ds);  
  
ds.Relations.Add("EmpDept", ds.Tables["Dept"].Columns["Deptno"],   
      ds.Tables["Emp"].Columns["Deptno"], false);  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-123">下列 Visual Basic 範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>填滿<xref:System.Data.DataSet>使用 Oracle `REF CURSOR`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-123">The following Visual Basic example demonstrates how to use an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> to fill a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> using an Oracle `REF CURSOR`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-124">這些範例會使用 Oracle Scott/Tiger 結構描述中所定義，需要下列 PL/SQL 封裝及封裝主體資料表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-124">These examples use tables that are defined in the Oracle Scott/Tiger schema, and require the following PL/SQL package and package body.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30aea-125">您必須建立這些要使用的範例伺服器上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-125">You must create these on your server to use the examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-126">在 Oracle 伺服器上建立下列 Oracle 封裝。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-126">Create the following Oracle package on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
```  
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE CURSPKG AS   
   TYPE T_CURSOR IS REF CURSOR;   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
      IO_CURSOR OUT T_CURSOR);   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
      DEPTCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR);  
END CURSPKG;  
/  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-127">在 Oracle 伺服器上建立下列 Oracle Package 內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-127">Create the following Oracle package body on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
``` 
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CURSPKG AS   
    PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
                               IO_CURSOR OUT T_CURSOR)   
    IS   
        V_CURSOR T_CURSOR;   
    BEGIN   
        IF N_EMPNO <> 0 THEN   
             OPEN V_CURSOR FOR   
             SELECT EMP.EMPNO, EMP.ENAME, DEPT.DEPTNO, DEPT.DNAME   
                  FROM EMP, DEPT   
                  WHERE EMP.DEPTNO = DEPT.DEPTNO   
                        AND EMP.EMPNO = N_EMPNO;   
        ELSE   
             OPEN V_CURSOR FOR   
             SELECT EMP.EMPNO, EMP.ENAME, DEPT.DEPTNO, DEPT.DNAME   
                  FROM EMP, DEPT   
                  WHERE EMP.DEPTNO = DEPT.DEPTNO;   
        END IF;   
        IO_CURSOR := V_CURSOR;   
    END OPEN_ONE_CURSOR;   
    PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
                                DEPTCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR)   
    IS   
        V_CURSOR1 T_CURSOR;   
        V_CURSOR2 T_CURSOR;   
    BEGIN   
        OPEN V_CURSOR1 FOR SELECT * FROM EMP;   
        OPEN V_CURSOR2 FOR SELECT * FROM DEPT;   
        EMPCURSOR  := V_CURSOR1;   
        DEPTCURSOR := V_CURSOR2;   
    END OPEN_TWO_CURSORS;   
END CURSPKG;  
 /  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-128">此 Visual Basic 範例執行傳回兩個的 PL/SQL 預存程序`REF CURSOR`參數，並填入<xref:System.Data.DataSet>使用傳回的資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-128">This Visual Basic example executes a PL/SQL stored procedure that returns two `REF CURSOR` parameters, and fills a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> with the rows that are returned.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
  
' GetConnectionString() returns a connection string for  
' the data source.  
  
    Dim connString As New String(GetConnectionString())  
    Dim ds As New DataSet()  
    Dim conn As New OracleConnection(connString)  
    Dim cmd As OracleCommand = conn.CreateCommand()  
  
    cmd.CommandText = "CURSPKG.OPEN_TWO_CURSORS"  
    cmd.CommandType = CommandType.StoredProcedure  
    cmd.Parameters.Add("EMPCURSOR", OracleType.Cursor).Direction = _  
       ParameterDirection.Output  
    cmd.Parameters.Add("DEPTCURSOR", OracleType.Cursor).Direction = _  
       ParameterDirection.Output  
  
    Dim da As New OracleDataAdapter(cmd)  
    da.TableMappings.Add("Table", "Emp")  
    da.TableMappings.Add("Table1", "Dept")  
    da.Fill(ds)  
  
    ds.Relations.Add("EmpDept", ds.Tables("Dept").Columns("Deptno"), _  
      ds.Tables("Emp").Columns("Deptno"), False)  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-129">在使用後<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>來執行`Fill`或`FillSchema`作業，`DataColumn.ReadOnly`屬性永遠傳回 false，不論是否更新的資料行可以是，因為 Oracle 伺服器不會傳回這項資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-129">After using the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> to perform a `Fill` or `FillSchema` operation, the `DataColumn.ReadOnly` property always returns false, regardless of whether a column can be updated or not, because the Oracle server does not return this information.</span></span>

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-133">當您建立的執行個體<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>，下列的讀取/寫入屬性設定為其預設值，在資料表中所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-133">When you create an instance of <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>, the following read/write properties are set to their default values, as shown in the table.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="30aea-134">屬性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-134">Properties</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="30aea-135">預設值</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-135">Default value</span></span>|  
|----------------|-------------------|  
|<xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingMappingAction%2A>|`MissingMappingAction.Passthrough`|  
|<xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A>|`MissingSchemaAction.Add`|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-136">您可以變更任何屬性個別呼叫透過這些屬性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-136">You can change the value of any of these properties through a separate call to the property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-137">下列範例會建立<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>並設定其部分屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-137">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDataAdapter()  
    Dim myOracleConnection As OracleConnection = New OracleConnection("Data Source=Oracle8i;Integrated Security=yes")  
    Dim custDA As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter  
    custDA.MissingSchemaAction = MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey  
  
    custDA.SelectCommand = New OracleCommand("SELECT DeptNo, DName FROM Dept", myOracleConnection)  
    custDA.InsertCommand = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                                            "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", myOracleConnection)  
    custDA.UpdateCommand = New OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = :pDeptNo, DName = :pDName " & _  
                                            "WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", myOracleConnection)  
    custDA.DeleteCommand = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", myOracleConnection)  
  
    custDA.InsertCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
    custDA.InsertCommand.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.VarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.VarChar, 14, "DName")  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo").SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
    custDA.DeleteCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo").SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static void CreateOracleDataAdapter()   
{  
    OracleConnection myOracleConnection = new OracleConnection("Data Source=Oracle8i;Integrated Security=yes");  
    OracleDataAdapter custDA = new OracleDataAdapter();  
    custDA.MissingSchemaAction = MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey;  
  
    custDA.SelectCommand = new OracleCommand("SELECT DeptNo, CompanyName FROM Dept", myOracleConnection);  
    custDA.InsertCommand = new OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, CompanyName) " +  
                                            "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pCompanyName)", myOracleConnection);  
    custDA.UpdateCommand = new OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = :pDeptNo, CompanyName = :pCompanyName " +  
                                            "WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", myOracleConnection);  
    custDA.DeleteCommand = new OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", myOracleConnection);  
  
    custDA.InsertCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
    custDA.InsertCommand.Parameters.Add("pCompanyName", OracleType.VarChar, 14, "CompanyName");  
  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("pCompanyName", OracleType.VarChar, 14, "CompanyName");  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo").SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
  
    custDA.DeleteCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo").SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-141">這個實作<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>建構函式<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>屬性中指定的值為`selectCommand`參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-141">This implementation of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> constructor sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property to the value specified in the `selectCommand` parameter.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-142">當您建立的執行個體<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>，下列的讀取/寫入屬性設定為其預設值，在資料表中所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-142">When you create an instance of <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>, the following read/write properties are set to their default values, as shown in the table.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="30aea-143">屬性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-143">Properties</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="30aea-144">Initial value</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-144">Initial value</span></span>|  
|----------------|-------------------|  
|<xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingMappingAction%2A>|`MissingMappingAction.Passthrough`|  
|<xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A>|`MissingSchemaAction.Add`|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-145">您可以變更任何屬性個別呼叫透過這些屬性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-145">You can change the value of any of these properties through a separate call to the property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-146">下列範例會建立<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>並設定其部分屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-146">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDataAdapter()  
    Dim myOracleConnection As OracleConnection = New OracleConnection("Data Source=Oracle8i;Integrated Security=yes")  
    Dim myOracleCommand As OracleCommand = New OracleCommand("SELECT DeptNo, DName FROM Dept", myOracleConnection)  
    Dim custDA As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter(myOracleCommand)  
    custDA.MissingSchemaAction = MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey  
  
    custDA.InsertCommand = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                                            "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", myOracleConnection)  
    custDA.UpdateCommand = New OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = :pDeptNo, DName = :pDName " & _  
                                            "WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", myOracleConnection)  
    custDA.DeleteCommand = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", myOracleConnection)  
  
    custDA.InsertCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
    custDA.InsertCommand.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.VarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.VarChar, 14, "DName")  
    custDA.UpdateCommand.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo").SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
    custDA.DeleteCommand.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo").SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
End Sub  
```  
  
