## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="30aea-151">這個實作<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>很有用的應用程式，必須呼叫`Fill`二或多個方法<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30aea-151">This implementation of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> can be useful in an application that must call the `Fill` method for two or more <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
